name: Many Flyers
overview: Many Flyers will take the hassle out of travel planning, especially for groups. Booking travel online should be a fun experience where you can find the best options for you based on your criteria - searching for flights isn’t just about finding the cheapest option. Maybe you want to go to Napa with friends, and you need to all get to SFO at the same time. Maybe you want a layover at DTW so you can catch a Michigan game on your way across the country. Maybe you’ve never booked travel online before. If you’re in any of those situations, existing travel booking sites will make you want to cry. Or throw your computer across the room. Many Flyers will change that.
